Text: This is definitely not anything like TROOPS. In fact, Kevin Rubio, the guy who made and wrote the first TROOPS, had nothing to do with this. This is absolute crap. Just to prove how stupid this is, stormtroopers go to a domestic dispute with Aliens and Predators. That's bad enough by itself, considering this is the Star Wars universe, but to make it worse, it's simply NOT FUNNY. Very dissapointing.
Have no idea why it double posted. Sorry about that.
